Usage: quill [flags] <template-name>

Flags:
  -autoescape string
    	output escaping strategy: "off" (default, source emission) or "html" (default "off")
  -data string
    	JSON file with the render variables (an object); "-" reads stdin
  -root string
    	template root directory the loader resolves names under (default ".")
  -strict
    	strict-undefined handling; -strict=false enables lenient migration mode (default true)
  -version
    	print the version and exit
